Home > Entertainment > Soulja Boy &"Cash Me Ousside" Girl Danielle Bregoli Take Shots At One Another On Twitter Soulja Boy &"Cash Me Ousside" Girl Danielle Bregoli Take Shots At One Another On Twitter 0 0 Posted by Kevin Goddard , Feb 20, 2017 at 11:13pm Soulja Boy & Danielle Bregoli have some choice words for one another. Now that his boxing match with Chris brown looks to be over, Soulja Boy is now moving on to other things…. like beefing with “cash me ousside” viral star Danielle Bregoli. Before she had some choice words for the Kylie & Kim Kardashian Monday morning, Danielle took to twitter last night for a simple ”fuck you @souljaboy.” While it’s unclear at the moment where the hostility came from &/or why, Soulja Boy wasn’t going to just sit back & take it. — BHAD BHABIE (@TheBhadBhabie) February 20, 2017 Shortly after, the SODMG rapper took to his twitter to give the kind gesture right back to her…“Fuck you too little ugly bitch” he tweeted. So being from the streets as she says, Danielle had to get the last word in by throwing some shade about his money & how she’s made more than him in the past week than he did all of last year. “I MADE MORE MONEY THIS WEEK THAN YOU DID LAST YEAR. GO CUDDLE WITH YOUR DRACO HO @souljaboy” Danielle tweeted. Check out the exchange (below) and we’ll keep you posted if anything more transpires from it.
